metadata.name: Darling Betty
metadata.description: This is a custom 1:1 illustration under the Darling Odlildeeds series commissioned by the Stacie A Buhler the influential creator of Ugly Betty & Bert sketches. This NFT is not only a token of appreciation, but also alliance as creatives sharing their hearts and stories on the blockchain. We see each other reflect artfully in the ether. This is an original work under the Correspondent token, also giving access to the first edition of the horny comic along with Darling's confessional findings on feminine pleasure. <3
